item.title: CVE-2020-1895|2024-08-04T06:53:59.862Z -- facebook -- instagram%20for%20android
item.description: A large heap overflow could occur in Instagram for Android when attempting to upload an image with specially crafted dimensions. This affects versions prior to 128.0.0.26.128.
